title: Labasa College Magazine 2008_The Labasan
description:
The 2008 version of the annual magazine for the premier academic institution (High school) of the northern division of Fiji Islands - Labasa College. It's known as the 'Labasan' (I know, we're working on that) and is pronounced as the 'Lambasan'.

To all you people who are affiliated with Labasa College for some or the other reason, this is for you to have a look.

Psst....I'm the guy receiving the big wooden shield on the front page. Yay!
